Clara HETRICK, Appellant, v. Fred HARVEY et al., Appellees. No. 10107. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit. Dec. 7, 1945. Harrison & Marshman, of Cleveland, Ohio, for appellant. Paul Clarke, of Cleveland, Ohio, for ap-pellees.

Before HICKS, SIMONS, and ALLEN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The motion for the defendant-appellee The Atchison, Topeka and Santa Fe Railway Company herein to dismiss the appeal having been considered by the court, it is now ordered that the said appeal be and the same is dismissed.
